{
  "chapter": 57,
  "chapter_summary": "第五十七回\"杀手三剑\"。方宝玉闯入白水宫，先与长发少女交锋对话，拒脱衣裳。随后在岩洞密道中历经酷热磨难，险些虚脱，以意志力克服重重机关。他先后遭遇三道杀手考验：第一道为神秘剑客施展的海南派\"扭转乾坤杀手剑\"，剑下留情并赠剑于宝玉；第二道为苍老剑客施展的东海白衣人绝招，杀气凝重却无杀机；第三道尚未揭晓。宝玉凭对白衣人招式的深刻理解，精准分析出剑上杀气与心中杀机的区别，令苍老剑客叹服。白水宫机关之诡秘、人物之神秘，令宝玉疑云重重。章节末尾，宝玉在岩洞中发现刻有\"软红山庄，星星小楼\"的字样，与蒋笑民遗书暗合。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "我知道不但我急着见你家宫主，你家宫主也同样在等着见我，我若真的原路退回，你们就惨了，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "站住，我还有话问你。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "问吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你可知咱们宫主在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "既然已到了水宫，还怕寻不着宫主？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这水宫中道路穷极变化，消息机关更是巧夺天工，到了水宫，却见不着娘娘的人也不知有多少，被困在消息机关中永生也走不出来的，也有许多……要见我家娘娘，哪有你想的那般容易？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "那些人是那些人，我是我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你虽和那些人有点不同，但也未必……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "虽然未必，我也得试试。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "只要你脱下衣服，我这就带你去见娘娘，否则……哼！你非但不知要吃多少苦，还可能永远也找不到。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "无妨。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你……你莫要后悔！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "这衣服我本来脱了也无妨，但瞧你如此着急，竟不惜千方百计要我脱衣裳，这其中显见大有文章，所以……宁可后悔，我也是不脱的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "白水宫主在哪里？方宝玉求见！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这么热，你还不脱衣服么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "此地这么黑，你纵然脱了衣服，也没有人会瞧见的，你还害什么羞？……你为什么还不脱？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "你为什么定要我脱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "就因为你不脱，所以就定要你脱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "你可知我为什么不脱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我正想听听你为何如此顽固？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "一个男人，若是赤身露体地处于许多个赤身露体的女子中，他纵有再强的意志，也会崩溃，他的自尊与自信也会完全消失，他简直任何事都不能做了。你们自然也深知此点，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "所以，这正是你们攻心的战略。只怕已不知有多少男人落在你们的圈套中，但是我方宝玉……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "好，方宝玉，算你聪明……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "好，你能走过这么一段路，真不愧为方宝玉！但——方宝玉，可知道你现在已到了哪里？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "已走到你面前。",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我让你瞧瞧也罢……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "我早就告诉过你，此间密道，穷极变化，此刻你总该相信了吧？你还不脱下衣服？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "不！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "只要你脱下衣服，立刻就可以见着我家娘娘，立刻就可以泡在水里，又清又凉的水，你要泡多久就泡多久，要喝多少就喝多少。你为何还要逞强？你这样撑下去，死了又有谁夸你半句？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "text": "你放心，我不会死的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_yu_sheng_nv",
      "speaker_name": "黑暗中女子",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "好，我看你还能挨多久！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方宝玉，你醒来了？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "方宝玉，你现在总该知道你不是铁打的身子，你也有倒下去的时候。现在，你可愿服了么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "水，水……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这杯子里满满的盛着杯玫瑰的花露，方才我已滴了三滴在你脸上，就只三滴，已使你自昏迷中苏醒，它的清香甜美，你虽在昏迷中，也该感觉得出。只要你服了，你就可将这满满的一杯全喝下。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "花露？……玫瑰……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "清冷的水珠，我再让你尝尝……",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "text": "不，不答应，不服！",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_fa_shao_nv",
      "speaker_name": "长发少女",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "真是牛一样的脾气！好，你既然还要受罪，也怨不得我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你居然能到达这里，也算不易。但你却要知道，这里距离水宫中枢虽已近，但剩下的这一段路却更艰辛，你千万不可大意。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你年纪轻轻，有此毅力，也算难能可贵。只要你抱定决心，你吃的苦就不会是白吃的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "现在，你还能站起来么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "能。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "既能站起，为何还不站起往前走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "阁下为何不让小可拜见尊颜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你不必瞧我的脸，你只要瞧着我的剑。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你是否早已见过这一招了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你若非早已见过这一招，此刻便难免伤在剑下。我要以此等杀手取你性命，你为何还要谢我？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "剑下是否留情，方宝玉岂能不知？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "纵然留情，但也足以取你之命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "但在下此刻却还是活着的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错，你现在还是活的。你见过这一招已有两次，居然还能活着，世上能伤你的剑法，只怕已不多了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "不多？……是否也不少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "嗯，也不少，至少还有三种。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "text": "为何不令在下领教领教？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_ke_shen_yin",
      "speaker_name": "神秘剑客",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "你着急什么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "这一招你已见过？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "是谁曾向你施出这一招？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "铁金刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "铁金刀？他……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "那一刀虽是铁金刀击出，却又等于不是。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "此话怎讲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "只因铁金刀不过是受他人所命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "白衣人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "正是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "那一招可是与我这一招完全相同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "十九相同，却又有一最大不同之处。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "此话又怎讲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "那一招杀气最盛处便也是破绽所在之处，他的体温自破绽处透出，所以我就冒险攻向此点，果然成功。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "但阁下出手前并未十分蓄力，心情也不紧张，是以阁下的体温完全正常，由此可见，阁下剑上虽有杀气，心中却并未伏杀机……阁下剑上的杀气，只不过是自这一招本身发出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "哦！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 512
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "只因阁下心中并无杀机，所以施出这一招时，心与剑便未能合二为一，于是阁下剑上的杀气便自然不及铁金刀那一刀上的刚猛。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "所以如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "那一刀击出时必见血光，所以我被迫取了他的性命，只因那其间根本别无选择之余地，而阁下这一剑，却使我根本无法施出杀手！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不错，剑上若无伤人之意，便也决不会引动别人剑上的杀机，这正是剑道中至高无上的道理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "但……阁下既无伤人之意，却又为何要以此等杀手来对付在下？这岂非互相矛盾？在下委实不解。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不解便也罢了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "还有，这一招本是白衣人不传之秘，普天之下，本无别人知道这一招的奥秘，阁下却又是从哪里学来的？在下更是不解。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "不久你就会知道了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "方宝玉",
      "listener": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "text": "不久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cang_lao_yu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "苍老语声",
      "listener": "char_fang_bao_yu",
      "text": "正是已不久……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    }
